{"lemma":"نُثارُ","slug":"نُثارُ","root":"ن.ث.ر","root_slug":"ن-ث-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ث-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39323","n39324"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8F%D8%AB%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39323","headword_ar":"نُثَارٌ","root":"nvr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What becomes scattered, strewn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersed, of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from, a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuvaArapN","text_ar":"نُثَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navarN","text_ar":"نَثَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, [but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munotavirN","text_ar":"مُنْتَثِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and, as some say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nivaArN","text_ar":"نِثَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) so the ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuvaArap","text_ar":"نُثَارَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wheat, and of barley, and the like: (Lh, M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuvaArN","text_ar":"نُثَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crumbs of bread,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of everything, that become scattered around the table:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crumbs"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the table"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that become scattered around:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuvaArapN","text_ar":"نُثَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) or this last,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what becomes scattered from the table, and is eaten in the hope of obtaining a recompense"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for preventing its being thrown away"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trodden under foot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lh, M, K. *)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","Msb","Lh","T","A"]},{"entry_id":"n39324","headword_ar":"نِثَارٌ","root":"nvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb,) signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of scattering, strewing, dispersing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throwing dispersedly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[anything,] (Lth, T, A, Msb,) [and particularly fruits and the like, such as] walnuts and almonds and sugar [and money, &c., on festive occasions,] and grain. (Lth, T.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahidotu nivaAra fulaAnK","text_ar":"شَهِدْتُ نِثَارَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was present at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I witnessed, such a one's scattering"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, A) of fruits, &c. (Lth, T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~aA","text_ar":"كُنَّا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY nivaArihi","text_ar":"فِى نِثَارِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We were at his scattering."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is scattered, strewn, dispersed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrown dispersedly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, TA,) of such things as sugar and fruits and the like, (A, TA,) [and money, &c., on festive occasions;] a subst., (A, TA,) in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manovuwrN","text_ar":"مَنْثُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makotuwbN","text_ar":"مَكْتُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navarN","text_ar":"نَثَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munotavarN","text_ar":"مُنْتَثَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSanotu mina Aln~ivaAri","text_ar":"اَصَنْتُ مِنَ النِّثَارِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I obtained"},{"kind":"text","text":"[somewhat]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the scattered"},{"kind":"text","text":"[sugar or fruits &c.]. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aSabonaA mino navari fulaAnK $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"مَا اَصَبْنَا مِنْ نَثَرِ فُلَانٍ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We did not obtain aught of such a one's scattered things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"such as sugar and fruit. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuvaArN","text_ar":"نُثَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the first of the senses explained above. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","Lth","T","TA"]}]}}